                </p>
                <%= link_to "Clear all filters", products_path(country: params[:country]), class: "mt-2 inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500" %>
